    "description": "**High Speed USB 2.0** clock noise. Shows up at multiples of 480 MHz. The USB clock is 48 MHz * 10 = 480 MBit/s. \n\nThis type of noise is quite commonly seen at 480/960 MHz on USB powered SDR devices."
